# My First React App

## Description
This is a simple React application created using Create React App. It displays a welcome message on the browser.

## Technologies Used
- React
- JavaScript
- HTML
- CSS
- Node.js
- npm

## Features
- React application setup using Create React App
- Displays "Welcome the first session of React"

## Installation

Clone the repository:

```bash
git clone https://github.com/your-username/myfirstreact.git
```

Go to the project folder:

```bash
cd myfirstreact
```

Install dependencies:

```bash
npm install
```

Run the application:

```bash
npm start
```

Open your browser and visit:

```
http://localhost:3000
```

## Output

```
Welcome the first session of React
```
